participants.title: Agile Product Owner & Product Development Consultant

messages.message: Hahaha. Hey Brian. How goes it? How work, wife, life?
Excellent. Just got a new job at Charles Schwab. Iga is good. Doing a big of work on side in the interim. We should come visit.

Nice, what sorta work for chucky swab? I still tell Iga's parrot joke (and credit her).

For sure! December is a mess but Jan feb is looking better for a visit. U guys still in AZ?
Security work. The kind my NDA prevents me from talking about. Iga appreciates your jokes. Still in AZ. How's life on your end? I recently realized I am from another dimension

Life on my end is good. Still in seal beach and had a bit of the downies after DNA Spectrum blew up after 4 years of my life but finnaly over it and making time at a Corp gig for the next 18 months doing some fun work.
Does your dimension have a number? I thought there were only 10 +-1
At least 5 or 6. I've transcended time.
Big thanksgiving dinner in AZ tomorrow?
Going to see family in Charleston.
